Built-in policy: Configure storage accounts to disable public network access

Definition ID: a06d0189-92e8-4dba-b0c4-08d7669fce7d
Effect: Modify or Deny – sets properties.publicNetworkAccess = Disabled and disables all public endpoint traffic.

Manual configuration via Portal:

Storage Account → Networking (Security + networking).
Under Public network access, select Disabled.
Save to block all public access.


