Built-in policy: Configure Azure SQL Server to disable public network access

Definition ID: 28b0b1e5-17ba-4963-a7a4-5a1ab4400a0b
Effect: Modify or Deny – sets publicNetworkAccess = Disabled, blocking all public IP connectivity.

